{"tid":1145442,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人嘅願望係移民？","createTime":"2019-05-08T17:13:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-10T08:33:55.000Z","uid":199547,"like":26,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"6156def50289961881f396ed1b04ad31adbfbc2f","tid":1145442,"uid":199547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T17:13:53.000Z","msg":"本身細個嗰陣被吹奏香港幾好點好咁，以為香港人生活富裕，舒服，仲諗住喺香港過世<br />\n<br />\n但係人大咗就發現香港呢笪地方好似大陸，大陸人爭資源，逃販條例，分分鐘被人捉返上大陸受審<br />\n<br />\n南亞狗周街打劫恰人，再望望立法會班建制垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />都唔知收咗唔知幾多維穩費<br />\n<br />\n所以好想第時有條件就移民去外國重新開始<br />\n有冇人都係對香港冇乜希望好想走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9c453894ec29c8a65573d0e7a1f71fd96d24b80","tid":1145442,"uid":217460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T17:14:50.000Z","msg":"我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55aa206f49051572c7bf88926bf4f79d07788067","tid":1145442,"uid":199547,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T17:21:44.000Z","msg":"移民嘅國家唔需要好發達，生活節奏慢啲，啲人質素好啲，平平地咁買間屋同另一半過世就夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6365107e245140c5ee1a258f7f019e5eebdeaa4e","tid":1145442,"uid":5852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T17:24:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71eb0921baa4a87567487d481668fc8751983c6a","tid":1145442,"uid":211633,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T17:27:22.000Z","msg":"依家去二三缐國家都唔太介意，去新加坡，德國，非英語歐洲國家都好過香港，最多去台灣算，香港非人住"},{"pid":"d3ede70bfa5d1259823d147cf41acabab9ae9041","tid":1145442,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T17:28:54.000Z","